com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.generic
Interface GenericUnit

All Known Implementing Classes:
GenericUnitImpl
public interface GenericUnit

A representation of the model object 'Unit'. The GenericUnit usually contains a Generic capability. It doesn't add any attributes over the core Unit. It exists to help GMF and SOA Deploy to attach custom validation and deployment logic.
